---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import go from "../images/go.svg";
import linkedIn from "../images/linkedin.svg";
import x from "../images/x.svg";
import github from "../images/github.svg";
import mail from "../images/mail.svg";
---

<Layout
  title="Trust Jamin"
  description="Trust Jamin is a software engineer who is devoted to making the web easily accessible for everyone. here you'll find some of his previous projects,technical articles, community management endeavors,involvments in open source projects and pieces of information about him."
  keywords="code contributions,developer advocate, open source collaboration,technical Writing, community engagement,problem solver,software development,developer-communities, DevRel"
  image="/home.png"
>
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1><span>Hey 👋🏼, I'm</span> Jamin</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          software engineer deeply interested in bridging connections between
          developers and state-of-the-art technology. I build <a
            href="/projects#Engineering Projects">products</a
          > , and write <a href="/blog">technical articles</a>. In my free time , you can find me contributing to <a
            href="http://github.com/0xJamin"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">open-source</a
          > projects or developing <a href="/projects#Engineering Projects">solutions</a> for
          challenges I have previously encountered.
        </p>
        <p>
          Presently, I’m learning GoLang <Image
            src={go}
            alt="Go Icon"
            class="goLang"
          /> and I’m surprised 😮 at its inherent simplicity and remarkable
          performance as a programming language. As you must have possibly
          guessed, this portfolio is still a WIP. 🚧
        </p>
        <p class="socials">
          <a
            href="http://github.com/0xJamin"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <Image src={github} alt="Github Icon" class="" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="http://x.com/0xJamin"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <Image src={x} alt="Twitter Icon" class="" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="http://linkedin.com/0xjamin"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <Image src={linkedIn} alt="LinkedIn Icon" class="" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:hellotsjamin"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <Image src={mail} alt="Email Icon" class="" />
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }
  .goLang {
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .socials {
    margin-top: 50px;
  }
  .socials a {
    border: none;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .socials a:not(:last-child) {
    margin-right: 20px;
  }
</style>
